_sText: I won't really go much into detail for this map, so just try it and I hope you will like it :)... The inspiration is from de_Dust and de_Dust2, I've used the same textures, props and other things so the map should be similar to both dust maps. It has both outside and inside areas with some breakable doors over the entire map. <---( not too much so it's not annoying ) It has: 40 spawn points 2 Bomb sites: A, B I've tried optimizing the map as good as I could, so I hope you guys get good fps in game. > To install the map, simply put the new cstrike folder included in the folder over the old one and overwrite. Please comment for any suggestions, bugs and/or compliments? :D Enjoy!
